data.title: e-Absensi Luwu Timur
data.descriptions: The e-Absensi application provides a solution for the State Civil Apparatus (ASN) to conduct attendance electronically without having to queue in making absences entering and absentee home because this application can be installed on every smartphone with the Android platform. The e-Attendance application makes use of the smartphone's camera features to make attendance. This is intended to minimize the absence of attendance by employees so that it can improve the accuracy of employee absences.
